.note
  .note__icon announcement

  .note__text
    You are viewing a draft version of this resource.  Hitting save will replace the active version with this version. Auto-saving is disabled when you are viewing a draft version.

    .note__secondary
      - if @item_version.title.present?
        %strong #{@item_version.title}
      - else
        Draft
      was created on #{@item_version.created_at.strftime('%m/%d/%Y at %l:%M %p')}
      by #{@item_version.user.try(:email)}
